{"tid":1127221,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"以前真係睇少咗揸車嘅難度","createTime":"2019-04-27T02:57:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T01:26:08.000Z","uid":90004,"like":13,"dislike":126,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"00745436fa3cf61970eb75c1c9232ad4ade89c70","tid":1127221,"uid":90004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:57:57.000Z","msg":"學緊棍van<br />\n<br />\n第三堂學車，學完調頭泊位都覺得唔錯。<br />\n之後真正出街試下行車，真心淆撚左底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇位做動作真係要快<br />\n人多車多，啲狗又會衝出嚟。<br />\n慢少少後面啲車又呠到你暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又多死車<br />\n<br />\n不過棍波真係好有挑戰性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋教車師傅其實都真係幾攰respect"},{"pid":"2fd066cf60145a41989c1a6d288fd98b48b60bb6","tid":1127221,"uid":16061,"like":89,"dislike":4,"score":85,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T03:01:32.000Z","msg":"遲下你揸左幾個月就覺得自己識飛"},{"pid":"272ada9fd6280cea79996216440c1a6e5e5df993","tid":1127221,"uid":153,"like":169,"dislike":3,"score":166,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T03:03:17.000Z","msg":"教車師傅攰你老母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁撚樣都叫攰<br />\n我諗世上都無咩工係唔攰"},{"pid":"89ad99c101aa7dcfc39c71d1b3508c5bf90895ec","tid":1127221,"uid":90004,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2fd066cf60145a41989c1a6d288fd98b48b60bb6","tid":1127221,"uid":16061,"like":89,"dislike":4,"score":85,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T03:01:32.000Z","msg":"遲下你揸左幾個月就覺得自己識飛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T03:10:49.000Z","msg":"唔使識飛，只係希望可以快啲熟手，唔使諗咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9803cecdb97f28c62488f6d2d937bb612f88f56","tid":1127221,"uid":90004,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"272ada9fd6280cea79996216440c1a6e5e5df993","tid":1127221,"uid":153,"like":169,"dislike":3,"score":166,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T03:03:17.000Z","m